        <item>
            <title>网传 Galaxy Watch7 将有大变动，首次推出三款型号储存量加倍</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/26/galaxy-watch7-storage-rumor/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=galaxy-watch7-storage-rumor</link>
